\pard\f0\fs28  (x) Leaves narrow, small or medium, glabrous or nearly so above and often spotted, with rather dense plumose hairs beneath and on the margin; cauline leaves few or absent. Involucre with more or less numerous short, rigid simple eglandular hairs, more or less numerous stellate hairs and often a few glandular hairs. Achenes 3·5-4 mm, dark. Margins of receptacular pits slightly dentate, glabrous.
